{"word":"G2666 - καταπίνω - katapínō - kat-ap-ee'-no - Devour","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταπίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katapínō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-ap-ee'-no</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Devour</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விழுங்கு, அமிழ்"},{"paragraph":"to drink down, swallow down"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G4095 - πίνω - pínō - pee'-no/4095\">G4095</a>; to <i>drink down</i>, that is, <i>gulp entire</i> (literally or figuratively): - devour, drown, swallow (up).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2666/2666\">G2666</a>, <a href=\"#/G4095/4095\">G4095</a>, <a href=\"#/G4188/4188\">G4188</a>, <a href=\"#/G4213/4213\">G4213</a>, <a href=\"#/G4221/4221\">G4221</a>, <a href=\"#/G4222/4222\">G4222</a>, <a href=\"#/G4224/4224\">G4224</a>"}]}